Package: flowgate
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: init-system-helpers (>= 1.54~)
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-yaml, curl, blocky | adguardhome, angie | nginx, angie | libnginx-mod-stream, angie | certbot, angie | python3-certbot-nginx
Description: Network Flow Controller (DNS & Proxy Manager)
 Modern CLI tool for managing network flow infrastructure (DNS & Proxy).
 Supports Nginx/Angie (Layer 4 & 7) and Blocky/AdGuardHome (DNS).
 Automatically manages SSL certificates via Certbot (for Nginx) or
 native ACME (Angie).

Package: flowgate-web
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: init-system-helpers (>= 1.54~)
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, flowgate, python3, python3-fastapi, python3-uvicorn, python3-jinja2, python3-multipart, python3-passlib, python3-bcrypt, python3-pyotp, python3-itsdangerous
Description: Web UI for Flowgate
 Simple web dashboard to manage domains and services for Flowgate.
 Provides a graphical interface for the flowgate CLI tool.
